Install notes for pan/nesi at University of Auckland

/* 1) Use Cosmos.Make.defs.local in this folder as Make.defs.local in CHOMBO_HOME/lib/mk/Make.defs.local */
2) Compile with intel:
   module load GCC/4.9.2 (to get the correct intel compiler compatibility)
   module load intel
   module load intel-mpi
   module load HDF5                         # Then set path in Make.defs.local
   module load PAPI/5.4.3-intel-2017a
   (Note: you may need to run "module unload" on already loaded versions)
